00:05:41.600 --> 00:05:44.240
'Karvachaut'

00:05:44.360 --> 00:05:45.520
Hari ini.

00:05:46.240 --> 00:05:48.600
Tapi hanya Neeti yang
berhak berpuasa untukmu.

00:05:48.640 --> 00:05:50.800
